Playbook Execution Flow
====================
-> Creating a Security Group for the load balancer and EC2 instances with Playbooks
-> Add Nginx EC2 instances under the Load balancer
-> Extracting the private IPs of our EC2 instances in a file for further use.
-> Creating Dynamic Inventory
-> Preparing Ansible Global Config
-> Playbooks for Setting up Services in EC2 Instances
-> tomcat.yaml
-> Nginx.yaml
-> Memcached.yaml
-> MySQL.yaml
-> Tomcat.yaml
-> Site.yaml
